N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 40.41 - Rate of assessment

State Regulations

The rate of assessment to be paid pursuant to this Part
is hereby established as follows: 7 1/2 cents per hundredweight for the period

May 1, 1988, through April 30, 1989, on all milk received from producers, including each milk dealer's own production of milk handled for
sale. Notes
